<h1>Useful Words</h1>
<p>Whether you go to China, or just want to talk to people around campus, these words will help you blow them away with your language skills. Have fun!</p>
<table border="0" style="width: 500px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<h1 style="text-align: center;">Useful Mandarin Words</h1>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><br />Hello</td>
<td><br /><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/hello_mandarin.mp3">你好</a> (nǐ hǎo),</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>How are you?</td>
<td><br /><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/howareyou_mandarin.mp3">你好嗎?</a> (nǐ hǎo ma)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>I'm fine thanks, and you?</td>
<td><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/howareyou2_mandarin.mp3">我很好，你呢？</a> (wǒ hěn hǎo, nǐ ne)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>My name is...</td>
<td><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/name3_mandarin.mp3">我姓 ...</a> (wǒ x&igrave;ng ...)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><br />I love you</td>
<td><br /><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/iloveyou_mandarin.mp3">我愛你</a> (wǒ &agrave;i nǐ)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><br />Thank you</td>
<td><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/thanks1_mandarin.mp3">謝謝</a> (xi&egrave;xie)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><br />Good bye</td>
<td><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/soundfiles/mandarin/goodbye1_mandarin.mp3">再見</a> (z&agrave;iji&agrave;n)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
